window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Many people want to use the young champion of the great Raven clan for their own agenda.</b></p> <p>Yang is given a choice without a choice. Having survived the deadly trials at the Lion Academy, he is thrown into a new hell. From now on, he is a member of the Night Guardâ€”the hated masters of low warfare.</p> <p>Together with his new companion, he learns more about life in the Jade Empire and continues his ascent to the heights of power.</p> <p>The Ravens will spread their wings again!</p>"; 
